# st_snls  `v1.0.0`

jQuery st_snls script for create a empty container, Include custom style,custom option.
and callback when initial, Have fun!

See the [Demo Page](./preview.html).



## Quick start

1\.  Add latest jQuery and st_snls files

```html
<script src="../st_snls/module.js"></script>


<link href="../st_snls/css.css" rel="stylesheet">
```
![Quick start](data:image/png;base64,)


2\.  Create Elements

```html
<div class="fcl_lnls">
    <div class="fm-grp icon-inside">
        <label class="label inside req">住宿1</label>
        <input type="text" class="fm-ctrl default" placeholder="請輸入/選擇住宿" value="東京，2017/08/01，1晚" data-id='default'>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="fcl_lnls">
    <div class="fm-grp icon-inside">
        <label class="label inside req">住宿2</label>
        <input type="text" class="fm-ctrl default1" placeholder="請輸入/選擇住宿" value="東京，2017/08/01，1晚" data-id='default1'>
    </div>
</div>
```
3\. Active Module
```js
$('.default , .default1').st_snls({
    contentCss:'fz-md',
    customContent: '<select class="st_lnls location" data-label="入住地區:"></select> <div class="d-f m-t-xs">  <select class="st_lnls time" data-label="入住時間:"></select>  <select class="st_lnls night" data-label="共:"></select></div>',
    callback: {
        whenInit:function(elem){

        }
    }
})
```
![Create Elements](data:image/png;base64,)


4\. Enjoy!

![Preview st_snls](data:image/png;base64,)

## API


| Preview API             | Accept val                                      |
| -------------------     | ----------------------------------------------- |
| contentCss              | string                                          |
| customContent           | string                                          |
| callback                | object                                          |
| whenInit                | function                                        |
